data.description: Welcome to one of the most expansive residences in the neighborhood, thoughtfully enhanced with stunning updates throughout. This generously proportioned home not only boasts size but also efficiency, as the seller is graciously settling the outstanding balance on the tesla solar panels. Prepare to revel in the luxury of consistently low energy bills, adding an extra layer of financial ease to your homeownership experience. New HVAC system, washer, dryer, fridge, backyard furniture/umbrella, surround sound system and TV's convey!! Waiting for the updated pictures for brand new quartz countertops and backsplash!
